nonebot-plugin-picsbank 加载日志
项目 nonebot-plugin-picsbank 创建失败：
The current project's Python requirement (>=3.10,<4.0) is not compatible with some of the required packages Python requirement:
- nonebot-plugin-picsbank requires Python >=3.8,<3.11, so it will not be satisfied for Python >=3.11,<4.0

Because no versions of nonebot-plugin-picsbank match >0.2.0,<0.3.0
and nonebot-plugin-picsbank (0.2.0) requires Python >=3.8,<3.11, nonebot-plugin-picsbank is forbidden.
So, because nonebot-plugin-picsbank-test depends on nonebot-plugin-picsbank (^0.2.0), version solving failed.

• Check your dependencies Python requirement: The Python requirement can be specified via the `python` or `markers` properties

For nonebot-plugin-picsbank, a possible solution would be to set the `python` property to ">=3.10,<3.11"

https://python-poetry.org/docs/dependency-specification/#python-restricted-dependencies,
https://python-poetry.org/docs/dependency-specification/#using-environment-markers

项目 nonebot-plugin-mockingbird 创建失败：
The current project's Python requirement (>=3.10,<4.0) is not compatible with some of the required packages Python requirement:
- nonebot-plugin-mockingbird requires Python >=3.8,<3.10, so it will not be satisfied for Python >=3.10,<4.0

Because no versions of nonebot-plugin-mockingbird match >0.2.1,<0.3.0
and nonebot-plugin-mockingbird (0.2.1) requires Python >=3.8,<3.10, nonebot-plugin-mockingbird is forbidden.
So, because nonebot-plugin-mockingbird-test depends on nonebot-plugin-mockingbird (^0.2.1), version solving failed.

• Check your dependencies Python requirement: The Python requirement can be specified via the `python` or `markers` properties

For nonebot-plugin-mockingbird, a possible solution would be to set the `python` property to "<empty>"

https://python-poetry.org/docs/dependency-specification/#python-restricted-dependencies,
https://python-poetry.org/docs/dependency-specification/#using-environment-markers

teenstudy 加载日志
项目 teenstudy 创建失败：
The current project's Python requirement (>=3.10,<4.0) is not compatible with some of the required packages Python requirement:
- ddddocr requires Python <3.11, so it will not be satisfied for Python >=3.11,<4.0

Because no versions of teenstudy match >0.2.1,<0.3.0
and teenstudy (0.2.1) depends on ddddocr (>=1.4.7,<2.0.0), teenstudy (>=0.2.1,<0.3.0) requires ddddocr (>=1.4.7,<2.0.0).
Because ddddocr (1.4.7) requires Python <3.11
and no versions of ddddocr match >1.4.7,<2.0.0, ddddocr is forbidden.
Thus, teenstudy is forbidden.
So, because teenstudy-test depends on teenstudy (^0.2.1), version solving failed.

• Check your dependencies Python requirement: The Python requirement can be specified via the `python` or `markers` properties

For ddddocr, a possible solution would be to set the `python` property to ">=3.10,<3.11"

https://python-poetry.org/docs/dependency-specification/#python-restricted-dependencies,
https://python-poetry.org/docs/dependency-specification/#using-environment-markers

nonebot-plugin-starrail-calendar 加载日志
项目 nonebot-plugin-starrail-calendar 创建失败：
The current project's Python requirement (>=3.10,<4.0) is not compatible with some of the required packages Python requirement:
- nonebot-plugin-starrail-calendar requires Python ==3.10.9, so it will not be satisfied for Python >=3.10,<3.10.9 || >3.10.9,<4.0

Because no versions of nonebot-plugin-starrail-calendar match >1.0.4,<2.0.0
and nonebot-plugin-starrail-calendar (1.0.4) requires Python ==3.10.9, nonebot-plugin-starrail-calendar is forbidden.
So, because nonebot-plugin-starrail-calendar-test depends on nonebot-plugin-starrail-calendar (^1.0.4), version solving failed.

• Check your dependencies Python requirement: The Python requirement can be specified via the `python` or `markers` properties

For nonebot-plugin-starrail-calendar, a possible solution would be to set the `python` property to "3.10.9"

https://python-poetry.org/docs/dependency-specification/#python-restricted-dependencies,
https://python-poetry.org/docs/dependency-specification/#using-environment-markers
